quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  27,77,Kandi rwose yo (Qur’an) ni umuyoboro n’impuhwe ku bemeramana
  27,78,"Mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani wawe azabakiranura akoresheje itegeko rye. Kandi we ni Nyirimbaraga zihebuje, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  27,79,"Bityo (yewe Muhamadi) jya wiringira Allah! Mu by’ukuri, wowe uri mu kuri kugaragara"
  27,80,"Mu by’ukuri, ntushobora kumvisha abapfu (ukuri), ndetse ntiwanakumvisha ibipfamatwi umuhamagaro (wawe) mu gihe bateye umugongo bagenda"
  27,81,"Kandi ntiwanashobora kuyobora impumyi (uzikura) mu buyobe bwazo, ahubwo abowumvisha ni abemera amagambo yacu, bakaba ari na bo bicisha bugufi (Abayisilamu)"
  27,82,"N’igihe ijambo (ry’ibihano) rizabasohoreraho (abahakanyi), tuzabasohorera inyamaswa mu butaka ibabwira ko abantu batajyaga bizera amagambo yacu"
  27,83,"(Unibuke) umunsi tuzakoranya muri buri muryango (umat) itsinda ry’abahakanyeamagambo yacu, maze bakerekezwa (ku rubuga rw’ibarura)"
  27,84,"Kugeza ubwo bazagera (imbere ya Allah) akavuga ati \"Ese mwahakanye amagambo yanjye, kandi mutari muyasobanukiwe (ngo mumenye niba ari ukuri cyangwa ibinyoma), cyangwa mwakoraga iki (kindi)"
  27,85,"Nuko ijambo (ry’ibihano) ribasohoreraho kubera ibibi byabo, kandi ntibazashobora kugira icyo bavuga (biregura)"
  27,86,"Ese ntibabona ko twabashyiriyeho ijoro kugira ngo bariruhukemo, n’amanywa kugira ngo mubashe kubona (bityo mushake ibibabeshaho)? Mu by’ukuri, muri ibyo harimo ibimenyetso ku bantu bemera"
  27,87,"(Unibuke) umunsi impanda izavuzwa, maze ibiri mu birere no mu isi bigakangarana, uretse uwo Allah azashaka (guhumuriza). Kandi bose bazamugana bicishije bugufi"
  27,88,"Uzanabona imisozi wibwire ko iri hamwe, nyamara izaba igenda yihuta nk’ibicu. Ibyo ni ibikorwa na Allah, we watunganyije buri kintu. Mu by’ukuri, we azi byimazeyo ibyo mukora"